quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  104,4,"Mayee! Waxaa lagu tuuri burburisada."
  104,5,"Maxaa ku ogeysiiyeyna waxay burburisadu tahay?"
  104,6,"Waa Naar Alle oo la huriyey."
  105,1,"Mawaadan ogaan sida Rabbigaa u galay qoladii maroodiga?"
  105,2,"Sow kama uu dhigin dhagartoodii wax dhumay (ku dhammaaday jab iyo jah wareer),"
  105,3,"Oo ku soo dirin shimbiro guutoooyin ah,"